      <h1>Using Video Production to Promote Upselling to Existing Customers</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover how video boosts upselling strategies, helping brands connect with customers and showcase product value effectively.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>July 19, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 25, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
